column4: I am upgrading to 12.04 I got the message that some third party entiries in my source.list were disabled and I can reinable them after upgrade. can i enable them now so they will be installed with the upgrade?
honestly you probably won't use them. you can remember their names and grab them manually from the ubuntu software center after installation completes
how do I find their names?
sure you can google it and come up with the names..
